sub_title: Managing Director at Tziovanis Constantinou Hygiene Services Ltd
summary: Passionate Businessman with a great interest in technology and digitisation, specifically on how it can affect our daily and professional activities. My goal is to develop and implement new business strategies that will reshape the way business is conducted in the workplace, with the effect of yielding efficiency and positivity. I plan on furthering my education with an MBA or Management degree which I will conduct as soon as I collect enough business experience. I greatly value professionalism and innovation when it comes to different ways of thinking especially when it can be applied to already existing practices with the aim of prospecting my career. Above all, I love observing and exploring different peoples perspectives so that I can always learn and improve.
